    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/186" key="#Princeps">Sichachardus</persName> &lt;sic>
                        Dei previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3635" key="#Other_palatine_officer"
                            >Radelgis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">thesaurarii</rs> nostri, tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/1905" key="#Other_palatine_officer">Roffrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendario</rs> nostro <rs
                            key="#Gualdi #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >waldum</rs><rs key="#Palatium"> sacri nostri palatii</rs> finibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/3410" key="#Geographic_regions #Fiscal_property"
                            >Apulee</placeName>, locum qui dicitur Anglonem Maiorem; habet enim <rs
                            key="#Fines">fines</rs>: de parte una fine <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvius</rs> Latonte, id est fine via puplica que vadit ad <rs
                            key="#Casalia">casalem</rs> Patricii, inde qualiter fines discernit a
                            <rs key="#Gualdi">waldo</rs> Sancte Marie <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2317" key="#Mother_churches">Lucerine sedis
                            episcopalis</orgName>, inde fine fine &lt;sic> de <name ref="Radoaldus"
                            >Radoaldi</name>, inde fine fine &lt;sic> de Ioncarica, inde fines vadu
                        Petrosu, inde fine <rs key="#Rivers">flubiu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/3403">Fertore</placeName>,
                        reconiungente se in priora fine, tam quod ibi nostrum palatium tenuit quam
                        et quod inde <name ref="Grausus Bulgarensis">Grausonis Bulgarensis</name>
                        <rs key="#Inflow #Confiscation #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals">a sacro
                            nostro palatio concessum fuit</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation">pro merito culpe
                                <name ref="Grasulfus">Grasolfi</name> filii eius ac in nostrum
                            palatium evenit</rs>, in integrum tibi cum superius inferiusque, aquis
                        et viis concessimus, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc
                        nostrum roboreum preceptum cuncta que superius legitur habere et possidere
                        valeatis tam tu quamque heredes tui, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est
                        comitibus, gastaldis, vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3465" key="#Notary">Audoaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName> secundo anno, mense octubrio,
                        duodecima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
